        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Resources to Expand Partnerships for Opportunity and Workforce and Economic Revitalization Act or the RE-POWER Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides FY2022 supplemental appropriations to carry out Appalachian Regional Commission grant programs. The bill designates the funding as emergency spending, which is exempt from discretionary spending limits.</p>]]>
        </text>
